Ian Walter Nelson (23 April 1956, Wakefield, Yorkshire, England) – 23 April 2006) was an English new wave musician, and younger brother of Be-Bop Deluxe singer and guitarist Bill Nelson, whom he accompanied in different musical projects.
He was more than seven years younger than his brother Bill, who was present at the time of his birth, on 23 April 1956.
